{"date":"2022-04-06","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/22/3c/330055_AHxG5.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/22/3c/330055_AHxG5.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/22/3c/330055_AHxG5.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/22/3c/330055_AHxG5.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/22/3c/330055_AHxG5.jpg"},"summary":"他是于神话中留名的史上最强魔王瓦尔瓦托斯。\r\n\r\n他以王的身份走完了一生，由于强大而无比孤独，因此向往着平凡的生活，并在数千年后的世界转生成了村民亚德·梅特尔。\r\n\r\n然而，在他转生的未来，魔法文明不断衰落。魔法本身已经无比弱小。\r\n\r\n亚德与自己的第一个朋友兼儿时玩伴伊莉娜一起进入了魔法学园，虽然他尽力避免成为一个特殊人物，却藏不住自己过人的力量。\r\n\r\n敬畏他的人、想要亲近他的人络绎不绝，而过去令世界陷入恐惧的「魔族」也在暗地里展开了行动。\r\n\r\n前「魔王」究竟能否取得安稳而平凡的人生呢？\r\n\r\n波澜万丈的学园英雄奇幻故事，就此开幕！","name":"史上最強の大魔王、村人Aに転生する","name_cn":"史上最强的大魔王转生为村民A","tags":[{"name":"异世界","count":569,"total_cont":0},{"name":"龙傲天","count":434,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2022年4月","count":419,"total_cont":0},{"name":"轻小说改","count":336,"total_cont":0},{"name":"后宫","count":275,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":214,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SILVERLINK.","count":211,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战斗","count":199,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":138,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2022","count":135,"total_cont":0},{"name":"轻改","count":116,"total_cont":0},{"name":"开挂无敌","count":66,"total_cont":0},{"name":"厕纸","count":62,"total_cont":0},{"name":"小说改","count":56,"total_cont":0},{"name":"湊未來","count":38,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":34,"total_cont":0},{"name":"BLADE","count":31,"total_cont":0},{"name":"转生","count":17,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2022年","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"校园","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"恋爱","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"魔法","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"冒险","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"白毛","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"魔幻","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"横手美智子","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日漫","count":3,"total_cont"